job.title: DRDO Technician Recruitment 2021  Apply Online for 47 Vacancies in Rajasthan
job.body:
Total vacancies:47

Name of the Posts:

  • Technician

Description

New Central Government Jobs for ITI diploma holders have been published by Defence Research & Development Organisation for the vacancies of Technician. If you are searching for a government job in Rajasthan then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Technician, from 21.05.2021, and till 06.06.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Rajasthan and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee

  • Mode of application is EMAIL

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for Technician vacancies in Rajasthan, your ITI diploma must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply for these vacancies is 21.05.2021.
  •  Last date to apply in these vacancies is 06.06.2021

Age Limit Criteria

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 18 to 37  years old. 

DRDO Technician Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is 7000/-.

How to apply for DRDO Technician Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Technician. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of DRDO and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by DRDO.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
